{"id":"5b1fa9b25acfc40018633c01","typeName":"Pistol","category":"weapon","parentTypeChain":["Pistol","Weapon","CompoundItem","Item"],"handbook":{"categoryId":"5b5f792486f77447ed5636b3","price":15225},"common":{"name":{"zh":"GLOCK 18C 9x19 冲锋手枪","en":"Glock 18C 9x19 machine pistol"},"shortName":{"zh":"GLOCK18C","en":"Glock 18C"},"description":{"zh":"Glock18是一种配置了快慢机的Glock17衍生型号。这种武器经常与33发弹容量加长弹匣一起使用，当然也可以使用其他Glock17弹匣，适配10发、17发或者19发弹匣。这种手枪的套筒前部有开口，和其他长套筒型号相似，但其套筒是标准尺寸。四条逐渐加大的起防跳器作用的开口枪管切口（从后到前）向上喷射火药燃气，以此来帮助抑制这种高射速全自动手枪开火时膛口的上跳。","en":"The Glock 18 is a selective-fire variant of the Glock 17. The firearm is typically used with an extended 33-round-capacity magazine, although other magazines from the Glock 17 can be used, with available capacities of 10, 17, or 19 rounds. It has a keyhole opening cut into the forward portion of the slide, similar to the opening on the Glock long-slide models, although the Glock 18 has a standard-length slide. The keyhole opening provides an area to allow the four, progressively larger (from back to front) compensator cuts machined into the barrel to vent the propellant gases upwards, affording more control over the rapid-firing machine pistol."},"weight":0.231,"width":2,"height":1,"rarity":"Rare","backgroundColor":"black"},"properties":{"_raw":{"AdjustCollimatorsToTrajectory":false,"AimPlane":0.026,"AimSensitivity":0.65,"AllowFeed":true,"AllowJam":true,"AllowMisfire":true,"AllowOverheat":true,"AllowSlide":true,"AnimationVariantsNumber":0,"BackgroundColor":"black","BaseMalfunctionChance":0.1771,"BoltAction":false,"BurstShotsCount":3,"CameraSnap":5,"CameraToWeaponAngleSpeedRange":{"x":0.1,"y":0.2,"z":0},"CameraToWeaponAngleStep":0.1,"CanPutIntoDuringTheRaid":true,"CanQueueSecondShot":true,"CanRequireOnRagfair":false,"CanSellOnRagfair":true,"CanUnloadAmmoByPlayer":true,"CantRemoveFromSlotsDuringRaid":[],"CenterOfImpact":0,"Chambers":[{"_id":"5b1fa9b25acfc40018633c09","_mergeSlotWithChildren":false,"_name":"patron_in_weapon","_parent":"5b